OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1773321081
OL,3,CMajor five-storey hotel and spa plans
OL,4,Crecommended for approval
OL,6,FA revised planning application for a
OL,7,Ffive-storey hotel, conference centre
OL,8,Fand spa near Jersey Airport has been
OL,9,Frecommended for approval.
OL,11,FThe first plans submitted by Strive
OL,12,FHealth Club were narrowly refused by
OL,13,Ffour votes to three last November, due
OL,14,Fto concerns over the development's
OL,15,Fsize, alongside environmental, worker
OL,16,Faccommodation and traffic concerns.
OL,18,FThe updated proposal features almost a
OL,19,F10% reduction in floor space and a
OL,20,Flower building height, plus fewer
OL,21,Fhotel rooms and no employee homes.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1773321081
OL,3,CMajor five-storey hotel and spa plans
OL,4,Crecommended for approval
OL,6,FAlthough it now has the support of the
OL,7,FPlanning Officer, a final green light
OL,8,Fis still needed from the wider
OL,9,FPlanning Committee, with a meeting
OL,10,Fscheduled for Thursday 19 March.
OL,12,FPlans for the site in St Peter, next
OL,13,Fto the current Strive Health Club,
OL,14,Fwere first submitted in August 2025,
OL,15,Foutlining a four or five-star hotel
OL,16,Fwith up to 179 rooms, alongside a
OL,17,Frestaurant, cafe, three bars, a
OL,18,Fswimming pool and spa facilities.
OL,26,@yD@Prr
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1773321081
OL,3,CMajor five-storey hotel and spa plans
OL,4,Crecommended for approval
OL,6,FHowever, the development was refused
OL,7,Fon seven key grounds, including how it
OL,8,Fwould break the rules of the Bridging
OL,9,FIsland Plan (BIP) and be overbearing
OL,10,Fon the landscape as the island's
OL,11,Ftallest building outside of St Helier.
OL,13,FThe Committee said the previous
OL,14,Fapplication also failed to provide
OL,15,Fenough information regarding flood
OL,16,Frisks, drainage capacity, ecological
OL,17,Fimpacts on protected species, and the
OL,18,Fjustification for worker accommodation
OL,19,Foutside of a built-up area.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1773321081
OL,3,CMajor five-storey hotel and spa plans
OL,4,Crecommended for approval
OL,6,FThe BIP states that developments of
OL,7,Feight storeys or under can be
OL,8,Fsupported outside of town if they meet
OL,9,Fvarious conditions, including being
OL,10,F"appropriate to the townscape
OL,11,Fcharacter of the area" and "not
OL,12,Fadversely affecting the locality in
OL,13,Fterms of microclimate, wind
OL,14,Fturbulence, overshadowing, noise,
OL,15,Freflected glare, privacy and amenity
OL,16,Fof surrounding buildings".
OL,18,FChanges to the original plans include:
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1773321081
OL,3,CMajor five-storey hotel and spa plans
OL,4,Crecommended for approval
OL,6,FThe Planning Officer who has
OL,7,Frecommended the revised development
OL,8,Ffor approval, Sarah Jones, says: "The
OL,9,Fapplicant has submitted information to
OL,10,Fillustrate that the proposal is
OL,11,Fjustified, necessary and appropriate
OL,12,Fin its location, and this information,
OL,13,Falongside the advice provided by
OL,14,Fcolleagues in the Department for the
OL,15,FEconomy, is considered sufficient to
OL,16,Fmake the strategic case for the
OL,17,Fproposal.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1773321081
OL,3,CMajor five-storey hotel and spa plans
OL,4,Crecommended for approval
OL,6,F"Whilst the proposal would have an
OL,7,Fimpact on the open character of the
OL,8,Farea, this site is not considered as
OL,9,Fsensitive to change as other parts of
OL,10,Fthe countryside, reflective of its
OL,11,Flocation opposite the built-up area
OL,12,F(the operational area of the airport).
OL,14,F"The height is now similar to the
OL,15,Fmaximum height of the recently
OL,16,Fapproved Gama hanger proposed to be
OL,17,Fbuilt nearby. Notwithstanding, there
OL,18,Fremains some policy conflict arising
OL,19,Ffrom the negative visual impact this
OL,20,Fproposal will have on the character of
OL,21,Fthe area.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1773321081
OL,3,CMajor five-storey hotel and spa plans
OL,4,Crecommended for approval
OL,6,F"In its favour, the development will
OL,7,Fexpand on the range of visitor
OL,8,Faccommodation available on the island
OL,9,Fand, based on the advice of colleagues
OL,10,Fin the Department of Economy, would
OL,11,Fhave a "significant strategic impact"
OL,12,Fon the visitor economy."
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/7
